PREFIX mo: <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX sim: <http://purl.org/ontology/similarity/>
PREFIX dbpo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbpp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?auri ?aname ?puri ?pname WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adrienne_Bailon> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/hometown> ?puri . ?auri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/hometown> ?puri ; a ?type ; foaf:name ?aname . ?puri rdfs:label ?pname . FILTER (LANG(?pname)="en") FILTER ( REGEX (STR(?type),"music","i") ) FILTER (?puri != <http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States>) } LIMIT 10
